This thread is interesting to me because I have had messages in the past that mention &#39;seven&#39;. Just a couple of days ago on vacation in Las Vegas I had a strange encounter with the number seven resulting in a winning of $7.77, this got my wheels turning again about the number 7. So today I lit up the optical microphone and asked about the number 7. Attached is the file, the response is in the noise. You can also see the optical microphone in action on youtube and hear how it reproduces music.
 http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Ym0IXAvC7s

Dave: Is there any significance to the number 7?
Response: &quot;Yes, we want to break new ground&quot;

Dave


--- warrior18eii@... wrote:

From: Frank Ratka &lt;warrior18eii@...&gt;
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] New file uploaded to EVP-ITC
